{{version025}}
{{flavour|Summons between one and three minor (rank 5) demons.}}

'''Summon Minor Demon''' is a monster-only spell that summons 1-3 [[lesser demon]]s, with a duration dependent on the spellcaster's [[HD]].

{{monsters with spell}}

==Strategy==
This spell is usually the least of your problems.  In fact, it can in some cases be downright helpful, as the summoned demons may block [[line of sight]] to monsters that [[neqoxec|would otherwise do nasty things to you]].

[[Category:Monster spells]]
